high_descs: walk to face green kitchen island
wash and remove spatula from sink
walk to face green kitchen island
Walk forward to the stove top, turn left and walk just past the sink, then turn left towards the green dining table.
Pick up the spatula near the dirty pan on the table.

Put the spatula in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Turn around and walk back to the dining table.
Put the spatula back on the dining table, to the left of the dirty pan.
